  "response": "As of the latest information available, here are some popular options for headphones under Rs. 1000 in India:\n\n1. **boAt BassHeads 100 in-Ear Wired Earphones**: Known for their good bass quality and durability, these earphones are popular amongst budget-conscious consumers.\n\n2. **Realme Buds 2**: These earphones provide good sound quality, a comfortable fit, and strong bass, making them a great choice under Rs. 1000.\n\n3. **Sony MDR-EX150AP in-Ear Headphones**: Offering clear and balanced sound, good build quality, and a comfortable fit, these are a good option within this budget.\n\n4. **JBL C100SI in-Ear Headphones**: Known for delivering powerful bass and clear sound, these earphones are a popular choice.\n\n5. **Mi Dual Driver in-Ear Earphones**: Featuring good sound quality and dual drivers for enhanced audio performance, these earphones offer good value for money.\n\nNote that prices and availability might vary, so it's a good idea to check the latest reviews and prices from reliable sources before making a purchase.",
